window.docContents[139].resolve({"/Functors___-Monads-and-___do___-Notation/Varieties-of-Monads/#zh-monads-zoo-state-h002":{"contents":"\n\n基于元组的状态单子表示具有 σ 类型的状态的计算，生成 α 类型的值，作为采用起始状态并生成与最终状态配对的值的函数，例如σ → α × σ。\nMonad 操作通过计算正确地对状态进行线程化。\n\nA tuple-based state monad.Actions in StateM σ are functions that take an initial state and return a value paired with a\nfinal state.\n\nAdds a mutable state of type σ to a monad.Actions in the resulting monad are functions that take an initial state and return, in m, a tuple\nof a value and a state.\n\nExecutes an action from a monad with added state in the underlying monad m. Given an initial\nstate, it returns a value paired with the final state.\n\nRetrieves the current value of the monad's mutable state.This increments the reference count of the state, which may inhibit in-place updates.\n\nReplaces the mutable state with a new value.\n\nRecovers from errors. The state is rolled back on error recovery. Typically used via the <|>\noperator.\n\nFails with a recoverable error. The state is rolled back on error recovery.\n\nExecutes an action from a monad with added state in the underlying monad m. Given an initial\nstate, it returns a value, discarding the final state.\n\nSequences two actions. Typically used via the >>= operator.\n\nApplies a function to the current state that both computes a new state and a value. The new state\nreplaces the current state, and the value is returned.It is equivalent to do let (a, s) := f (← StateT.get); StateT.set s; pure a. However, using\nStateT.modifyGet may lead to better performance because it doesn't add a new reference to the\nstate value, and additional references can inhibit in-place updates of data.\n\nRuns an action from the underlying monad in the monad with state. The state is not modified.This function is typically implicitly accessed via a MonadLiftT instance as part of automatic\nlifting.\n\nModifies the value returned by a computation. Typically used via the <$> operator.\n\nReturns the given value without modifying the state. Typically used via Pure.pure.\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009函子、Monad 和  do  表示法\u0009单子的种类\u0009状态","header":"18.5.4.2. 基于元组的状态 Monad","id":"/Functors___-Monads-and-___do___-Notation/Varieties-of-Monads/#zh-monads-zoo-state-h002"},"/Source-Files-and-Modules/#files":{"contents":"Lean 中的最小编译单元是单个 源文件。\n源文件可以根据文件名导入其他源文件。\n换句话说，文件的名称和文件夹结构在 Lean 代码中很重要。\n\n每个源文件都有一个 导入名称，该名称源自其文件名和调用 Lean 的方式的组合：Lean 有一组根目录，它希望在其中查找代码，源文件的导入名称是从根目录到文件名的目录名称，带点 (.)散布并删除 .lean。\n例如，如果以 Projects/MyLib/src 作为根调用 Lean，则文件 Projects/MyLib/src/Literature/Novel/SciFi.lean 可以作为 Literature.Novel.SciFi 导入。\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考","header":"5. 源文件和模块","id":"/Source-Files-and-Modules/#files"},"/The-___grind___-tactic/Algebraic-Solver-_LPAR_Commutative-Rings___-Fields_RPAR_/#grind-ring-classes":{"contents":"用户可以通过提供以下 类型类 的实例（全部位于 Lean.Grind 命名空间中）来为自己的类型启用 ring 求解器：* Semiring* Ring* CommSemiring* CommRing* IsCharP* AddRightCancel* NoNatZeroDivisors* Field代数求解器将根据这些实例的可用性进行自我配置，因此不需要提供所有实例。\n当然，当某些代数求解器不可用时，代数求解器的功能将会降低。\n\nLean 标准库包含标准库中定义的类型的适用实例。\n通过提供这些实例，其他库也可以启用 grind 的 ring 求解器。\n例如，Mathlib CommRing 类型类实现 Lean.Grind.CommRing 以确保 ring 解算器开箱即用。\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009grind 策略\u0009代数工作室（交换环、域）","header":"16.8.1. 解算器 Type 类","id":"/The-___grind___-tactic/Algebraic-Solver-_LPAR_Commutative-Rings___-Fields_RPAR_/#grind-ring-classes"},"/The-___grind___-tactic/Linear-Integer-Arithmetic/#zh-grind-cutsat-h004":{"contents":"求解器规范交换（半）环表达式。\n\nCommutative (Semi)ring Normalization交换环归一化可以解决这个目标：example (a b : Nat)\n    (h₁ : a + 1 ≠ a * b * a)\n    (h₂ : a * a * b ≤ a + 1) :\n    b * a ^ 2 < a + 1 := by\n  grind\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009grind 策略\u0009线性整数算术","header":"16.7.4. 代数处理","id":"/The-___grind___-tactic/Linear-Integer-Arithmetic/#zh-grind-cutsat-h004"},"/Type-Classes/Instance-Declarations/#class-inductive-instances":{"contents":"许多实例具有函数类型：任何本身递归调用实例搜索的实例都是一个函数，任何具有隐式参数的实例也是如此。\n虽然大多数实例仅从其自己的实例参数投影方法实现，但类归纳类型的实例通常会对其一个或多个参数进行模式匹配，从而允许实例选择适当的构造函数。\n这是使用普通的 Lean 函数语法完成的。\n与其他实例一样，所讨论的函数不可用于其自身定义中的实例综合。\n\nAn instance for a sum class由于 DecidableEq α 是 (a b : α) → Decidable (Eq a b) 的缩写，因此可以直接使用其参数，如下例所示：inductive ThreeChoices where\n  | yes | no | maybe\n\ninstance : DecidableEq ThreeChoices\n  | .yes,   .yes   =>\n    .isTrue rfl\n  | .no,    .no    =>\n    .isTrue rfl\n  | .maybe, .maybe =>\n    .isTrue rfl\n  | .yes,   .maybe | .yes,   .no\n  | .maybe, .yes   | .maybe, .no\n  | .no,    .yes   | .no,    .maybe =>\n    .isFalse nofun\n\n\n\nA recursive instance for a sum class类型 StringList 表示单态字符串列表：inductive StringList where\n  | nil\n  | cons (hd : String) (tl : StringList)\n在以下定义 DecidableEq 实例的尝试中，在详细说明内部 if 时调用的实例综合失败，因为该实例不可用于其自己的定义中的实例综合：instance : DecidableEq StringList\n  | .nil, .nil => .isTrue rfl\n  | .cons h1 t1, .cons h2 t2 =>\n    if h : h1 = h2 then\n      if h' : t1 = t2 then\n        .isTrue (by simp [*])\n      else\n        .isFalse (by intro hEq; cases hEq; trivial)\n    else\n      .isFalse (by intro hEq; cases hEq; trivial)\n  | .nil, .cons _ _ | .cons _ _, .nil => .isFalse nofun\nfailed to synthesize instance of type class\n  Decidable (t1 = t2)\n\nHint: Type class instance resolution failures can be inspected with the `set_option trace.Meta.synthInstance true` command.\n但是，因为它是一个普通的 Lean 函数，所以它可以递归引用它自己显式提供的名称：instance instDecidableEqStringList : DecidableEq StringList\n  | .nil, .nil => .isTrue rfl\n  | .cons h1 t1, .cons h2 t2 =>\n    let _ : Decidable (t1 = t2) :=\n      instDecidableEqStringList t1 t2\n    if h : h1 = h2 then\n      if h' : t1 = t2 then\n        .isTrue (by simp [*])\n      else\n        .isFalse (by intro hEq; cases hEq; trivial)\n    else\n      .isFalse (by intro hEq; cases hEq; trivial)\n  | .nil, .cons _ _ | .cons _ _, .nil => .isFalse nofun\n\n\n","context":"Lean 参考\u0009Type 类别\u0009实例声明","header":"10.2.2. class inductive  的实例","id":"/Type-Classes/Instance-Declarations/#class-inductive-instances"}});